---
title: Caramelized Onion Meatloaf Sandwiches with Potato Wedges & Horseradish Dijonnaise
description: When it comes to comfort food, meatloaf used to sit squarely in the number one spot, followed closely by the next-day meatloaf sandwich. But this sandwich changes everything. Topped with a classic ketchup glaze, sliced meatloaf is stuffed between toasted sourdough along with caramelized onion and a horseradish Dijonnaise. With potato wedges on the side and more sauce for dipping, prepare to rave about the triumph of this long-time fave!
